@page "/opgaver/lol"

<div class="lol-container">
    <h1>League of Legends API Projekter</h1>
    <p class="intro-text">Udforsk forskellige League of Legends relaterede minispil og værktøjer.</p>

    <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
            <h2>Champion Overview</h2>
            <p>En komplet oversigt over alle League of Legends champions. Se detaljeret information om hver champion, 
                inklusiv deres klasser, udgivelsesdato, ressourcer og oprindelsesregion.</p>
            <div class="features-list">
                <span class="feature">✓ Detaljeret champion information</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Søgefunktion</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Filtreringsmuligheder</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/opgaver/lol/overview" class="project-link">Gå til Overview</a>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
            <h2>Guess the Splash</h2>
            <p>Test din League of Legends viden ved at gætte champions baseret på deres splash art! 
                Et sjovt spil der udfordrer din evne til at genkende champions fra deres artwork.</p>
            <div class="features-list">
                <span class="feature">✓ Tilfældige splash arts</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Point system</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Øjeblikkelig feedback</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/opgaver/lol/guess-splash" class="project-link">Prøv Guess the Splash</a>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
            <h2>Loldle</h2>
            <p>En Wordle-inspireret League of Legends gættespil! Gæt den hemmelige champion baseret på hints 
                om deres egenskaber, klasser og oprindelsesregion.</p>
            <div class="features-list">
                <span class="feature">✓ Detaljerede hints</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Farvekodet feedback</span>
                <span class="feature">✓ Ubegrænset antal gæt</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/opgaver/lol/loldle" class="project-link">Spil Loldle</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .lol-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .intro-text {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .projects-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .project-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .project-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .project-card h2 {
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-card p {
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .features-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature {
        color: #2c5282;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .project-link {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c5282 0%, #1a365d 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-align: center;
        transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .project-link:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d 0%, #2c5282 100%);
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .projects-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .lol-container {
            padding: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>

